data.description: Single level home with over 2,000SF and an oversized 3-Car Garage on a .4 acre lot ready to accommodate a shop!  4 BR, 2 BA home in a central Rathdrum location w/a city park right down the street! Open floor plan with large kitchen with pantry, island, breakfast bar, Quartz counters. Primary En-suite w/vaulted ceilings, blackout shades, fan, patio door, large bathroom w/dual sink vanity, spacious walk-in closet, and soaker tub with obscured windows behind it. 4th bedroom makes a wonderful office with glass doors but can easily serve as a bedroom given its large window and closet. Epoxy floor in the 3 car-garage w/ bonus workshop area, and man door. Covered porch, covered back patio and spacious wrap around open patio. A/C, custom window coverings, Gas Forced Air Furnace, Water Softener. Conc. curbing, front/rear sprinklers, custom stone patio by the firepit, beefy side gate to drive to future shop.
